msgstr ""

#: ../../../../../Wrapping/Python/vtkmodules/wx/wxVTKRenderWindowInteractor.py:314
msgid ""
"This prevents recursive rendering during wx.SafeYield() calls. wx."
"SafeYield() can be called during the ProgressMethod() callback of a VTK "
"object to have progress bars and other GUI elements updated - it does this "
"by disabling all windows (disallowing user-input to prevent re-entrancy of "
"code) and then handling all outstanding GUI events."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../../Wrapping/Python/vtkmodules/wx/wxVTKRenderWindowInteractor.py:321
msgid ""
"However, this often triggers an OnPaint() method for wxVTKRWIs, resulting in "
"a Render(), resulting in Update() being called whilst still in progress."
msgstr ""
